Jennie M. AVERY, as Administratrix of the Estate of Cora A. Kellam, Deceased, v. Helen RICKER. No. 178. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 3, 1930. C. J. Roberts, of Santa Fé, N. M., for appellant. F. O. Wester.fl.eld, of Albuquerque, N. M., and Fred W. Varney, oi Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, COTTERAL, and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed June 3,1930, per stipulation.
